@NODE Bugs

There are a few known bugs in this program. I will attempt to fix these as
soon as possible. If you find any new ones please let me know.

	*	Rather ugly memory usage when multiplying out big functions.
	
	*	Documentation rather out of date. Many features in the program
		have been changed but this document hasn't
	
@ENDNODE
